In the end, everything happened very quickly: In mid-May, Dr. Stefanie Kramer learned that she would be succeeding Lutz Feller in the Eggenfelden notary's office.
Just six weeks later, at the beginning of July, the doctor of law started work, and normal day-to-day business has long been running at full speed.
